graph LR
    ModelRegistryOp[Model Registry Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ModelRegistryOp -->|database backend<br/>REQUIRED| Database[PostgreSQL OR MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Service Mesh)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|service mesh<br/>OPTIONAL| Istio[Istio<br/>mTLS + Traffic Mgmt]
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|authentication<br/>OPTIONAL<br/>requires Istio| Authorino[Authorino<br/>K8s-native AuthN/AuthZ]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Monitoring)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|metrics<br/>OPTIONAL| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional - Platform)
    ModelRegistryOp -.->|route creation<br/>OPTIONAL| OpenShift[OpenShift<br/>Route API]

    %% Core Kubernetes Dependencies
    ModelRegistryOp -->|API calls<br/>CRD reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH Components (Consumers)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>create/manage registries| ModelRegistryOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|model tracking<br/>register models/artifacts| ModelRegistryOp
    KServe[KServe] -.->|model metadata<br/>fetch for inference| ModelRegistryOp
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving] -.->|model metadata<br/>fetch for serving| ModelRegistryOp

    %% Supporting Infrastructure
    CertManager[cert-manager] -.->|TLS certificates<br/>OPTIONAL| ModelRegistryOp

    %% Grouping
    subgraph "Required Dependencies"
        Database
        K8sAPI
    end

    subgraph "Optional Dependencies"
        Istio
        Authorino
        PrometheusOp
        OpenShift
        CertManager
    end

    subgraph "ODH Ecosystem (Consumers)"
        Dashboard
        Pipelines
        KServe
        ModelMesh
    end

    %% Styling
    style ModelRegistryOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style Database fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Authorino fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PrometheusOp fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
